              ╚───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╝

⚠️ To get started playing HellScape and your first Adrenaline(1), TYPE: .login

💀 There are 30 skills you can train for gold. These take roughly 20 minutes to finish and the bot will PM you with your XP and Gold. All giving the same XP and gold per hour, besides Slayer. !Slayer command is the best to start with for hourly Boss Fights.

💥 Boss Fights hourly scale by 10 levels each hour that you must have the Slayer level or higher to join.

⚔️ Battle Royale event starts every hour as well. Joining this sets you against a random opponent where your items or potion equivalent and pets will aid towards defeating them. ⚠️ [WARNING]: Joining this activity makes you a Player Killer and opens you up to be able to use the PvP shop on yourself and other players, some of which can camblock, mute, or close a user.


*-*-*-* Notes *-*-*-*
(1) Adrenaline is given out every 10 minutes; 20% if on camera and 10% if not. Random Events(2) will appear in the chat that requires Adrenaline to obtain them, either giving Gold, XP Lamps(3), Shards(4), or Keys(5). You can also buy more from !shop misc (#95) 
(2) Random Events! https://i.imgur.com/EdengB3.png Type the word within the brackets [] to loot them and the secondary part behind the "."prefix to use.
(3) XP Lamps can be used in any of the skills besides a few combat skills. Put them all into Slayer at the start by replacing "skill" with "slayer" when it prompts. Example of Genie's Lamp use: .genie slayer
(4) Shards (1x) are used for every boss you join or skill you train.
(5) Keys unlock the chest related to. Giving gold and an item spin.

